---
title: Cheesy Double Beef and Pork Hash with Cheddar and Sour Cream
description: Looking for a simple, hearty meal that packs a punch? We've got you covered! Flavourful beef and pork mix is coated in Enchilada Spice Blend and paired with herbaceous green onions, roasted potatoes and sautéed peppers. It's topped with tangy sour cream. Everyone in your family will enjoy this dish!

